title: Beijing 2022: Kaillie Humphries // Shaun White on last run // Paula Moltzan
description: The daily podcast from the Winter Olympic Games in China today has three of the best athletes from the United States. Kaillie Humphries shares the difficulties facing women competing in bobsleigh ahead of the monobob. Shaun White takes us through his emotional last day. And alpine skier Paula Moltzan explains why you should never give up on your passion.
